creator: GreenFlux Smart Charging
descriptionHtml:
Charge Assist is the perfect assistant for your electric vehicle - making EV charging as simple and quick as possible.

The app helps you to find publicly accessible chargers supported by the GreenFlux charging network. Charge Assist offers the fastest growing selection of chargers available in an app, with new chargers being added all the time!

Simply navigate towards a charger of your choice, start charging and pay automatically after your session ends. View a charger’s availability, its tariffs, the progress of your charge session and a host of other relevant information with just a few taps.

With Charge Assist, you can:
• Navigate to EV chargers worldwide
• Start and stop charge sessions
• View charging progress
• Filter based on power type and other features
• Scan QR codes to start charging immediately
• See charging tariffs
• See an overview of your previous charge sessions
• Use our Smart Charging technology

Charge Assist supports any modern payment method you may need, including credit cards, Apple Pay, Google Pay, and conventional EV charge cards.

Have feedback for us? Let us know by sending an email to hello@chargeassist.app!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: A brand new look and feel for your trusty charging companion!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We added some new features for you in this new release:
- added receipts for charge sessions done with mobile pay (credit card or alike);
- improved charge session graphs, and on the right fast chargers you could see the battery state;
- added a verification process for some charge cards, to mitigate the risk of misuse;
- added Greek language for our drivers in Greece;
- fixed the alarm notifications.
If you have any comments or remarks, please let us know.
